# Note: Secure units (24), Offshore schools (25), Service children's education (26),
# Miscellaneous (27) and Institution funded by other government department (56)
# have variable field applicability that requires further analysis of actual GIAS data
# before strong constraints can be added. No specific shapes are defined for these types
# in this version.


#################################################################
# Governance constraints
#################################################################

# hasGroupGovernanceAppointment is OWL-domain EstablishmentGroup (conceptual model).
# Current GIAS data constraint: all 28,692 UID-based group governance rows are MAT type.
# This SHACL shape enforces the current data constraint without narrowing the OWL domain.

epr:GroupGovernanceAppointmentSubjectShape
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf epro:hasGroupGovernanceAppointment ;
    sh:class epr:AcademyTrust ;
    sh:name "Group governance appointment subject"@en ;
    sh:message "The subject of hasGroupGovernanceAppointment must be an AcademyTrust. All 28,692 UID-based group governance rows in the current GIAS data are MAT type. If federation or other group-type governance is introduced, update this constraint."@en .


